System</b></font></center>

<hr>

<ul>
    <li><font size="4">Content Based Search: <br>
        <br>
        The Ability to recall events based on their content
        information</font>.<br>
        <br>
        </li>
    <li><font size="4">Example: An NBA year video showing the
        best events</font>:<br>
        <br>
        <font size="4">Total number of games in a year: 29 * 82 /
        2 + 91 = 1280 (games)<br>
        We need 1280 * 3 = 3840 (hours) to browse sequencially if
        using one video player</font><br>
        </li>
    <li><font size="4">A random access facicility can reduce this
        time to a few days</font>.<font size="4">As a member of
        VIMS family, Video Data Management System is capable of
        retrieving a video based on its content.</font><br>
        <hr>
